  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/8ad6c3120f5020ebf799870a3b6a8e79.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><br>More than 20 swords to choose , each with a unique attack style. Whether to motive your sword by the force of five elements or the power from underworld, it's all about a moment of thought.<br><br>Up to 90 kinds of splendid swordsmanship and 24 schools can be selected at your will. Slash the enemy through exquisite skills or unleash an abyss of blood engulfing everything? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/d2a77db2fe5149a38d252b6d5c0a67f3.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/d2a77db2fe5149a38d252b6d5c0a67f3.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a0d263fb3710d1bcdd57e3052dbd19c3.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a0d263fb3710d1bcdd57e3052dbd19c3.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a0d263fb3710d1bcdd57e3052dbd19c3.mp4?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/2819df2c84e511134c5dd00774d927cb.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><br>Over 70 treasures to 